# Round 3 — 15 Improvements Implementation Plan

## Phase 1: Critical Bug Fixes

### 1. Docker Fix
**Root cause:** `docker compose up -d` doesn't rebuild. Even with `--build`, `npm ci --production` downloads pre-built `better-sqlite3` binaries. Need to force native rebuild.
#### [MODIFY] [Dockerfile](file:///home/dtc/Desktop/SutraKnowledgeBase/Dockerfile)
- Add `RUN npm rebuild better-sqlite3 --build-from-source` after `npm ci`
- Keep `node:20-slim` base (glibc compatible)

### 13. Image Paste Fix
**Root cause:** Upload saves to `./uploads/images` (relative to CWD = `server/`), but static files served from `path.join(__dirname, '..', 'uploads')` = `SutraKnowledgeBase/uploads/`. **Different directories!**
#### [MODIFY] [upload.js](file:///home/dtc/Desktop/SutraKnowledgeBase/server/routes/upload.js)
- Use `path.resolve(__dirname, '..', '..', 'uploads', 'images')` as default
#### [MODIFY] [index.js](file:///home/dtc/Desktop/SutraKnowledgeBase/server/index.js)
- Ensure upload dir and static serving point to the same directory

### 6. Collection Dropdown Fix
**Root cause:** Collection controls are passed as prop through `Sidebar` → `FileTree`, but may not be rendering due to the restructure.
#### [MODIFY] [Layout.jsx](file:///home/dtc/Desktop/SutraKnowledgeBase/client/src/components/Layout.jsx)
- Debug and fix collection controls rendering + highlight active collection

### 12. Search Partial Match Fix
**Root cause:** Previous fix made search too strict (exact match only).
#### [MODIFY] [files.js](file:///home/dtc/Desktop/SutraKnowledgeBase/server/routes/files.js)
- Search by filename only (not content), use `LIKE %query%` for partial matching

### 14. Task List Rendering Fix
**Root cause:** `- [ ] wow\n[x] can be wow` — second line not treated as list item without `- ` prefix.
#### [MODIFY] [markdown.js](file:///home/dtc/Desktop/SutraKnowledgeBase/client/src/utils/markdown.js)
- Ensure task list items must be preceded by `- ` to be recognized

### 11. Duplicate Folder/File Name Prevention
#### [MODIFY] [folders.js](file:///home/dtc/Desktop/SutraKnowledgeBase/server/routes/folders.js)
- Check for existing folder with same name in same parent before creating
#### [MODIFY] [files.js](file:///home/dtc/Desktop/SutraKnowledgeBase/server/routes/files.js)
- Check for existing file with same name in same folder before creating

